<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #1a1a1a; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }
  .date-block { text-align: right; margin-bottom: 28px; color: #333; }
  .addressee { margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .re-block { margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 12px 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc; }
  .re-block p { margin: 2px 0; }
  .salutation { margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .statutes { margin: 16px 0; padding-left: 28px; }
  .statutes li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .requests { margin: 16px 0; padding-left: 28px; }
  .requests li { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .evidence-block { border: 1px solid #d0d0d0; padding: 14px 18px; margin: 24px 0; background: #fafafa; }
  .evidence-block ul { margin: 8px 0; padding-left: 20px; }
  .evidence-block li { margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 13px; }
  .evidence-block a { color: #1a56db; }
  .policy-note { font-size: 13px; color: #444; margin: 16px 0; padding: 10px 16px; border-left: 3px solid #1a56db; background: #f0f4ff; }
  .info-block { border: 1px solid #d0d0d0; padding: 14px 18px; margin: 24px 0; }
  .info-block table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; }
  .info-block td { padding: 4px 12px 4px 0; vertical-align: top; }
  .info-label { font-weight: bold; white-space: nowrap; width: 160px; }
  .signature { margin-top: 36px; }
  .cc-block { margin-top: 28px; font-size: 13px; color: #555; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 12px; }
  .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 11px; color: #888; }
  .sent-via { font-size: 12px; color: #666; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 24px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="date-block">
  {{ date }}
</div>

<div class="addressee">
  {{ broker_name }}<br>
  Data Privacy / Compliance Department<br>
</div>

<div class="sent-via">Sent via electronic mail</div>

<div class="re-block">
  <p><strong>Re: Request for Deletion of Personal Information</strong></p>
{% if region == 'EU' %}
  <p>Pursuant to the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and Applicable Data Protection Laws</p>
{% else %}
  <p>Pursuant to Applicable Federal and State Privacy Laws</p>
{% endif %}
  <p>Reference: {{ request_id }}</p>
</div>

<p class="salutation">Dear Data Privacy Officer or Authorized Representative,</p>

{% if region == 'EU' %}
<p>I am writing to formally exercise my rights as a data subject under the General Data Protection Regulation (EU) 2016/679 and applicable national data protection legislation. This letter constitutes a formal request for the erasure of all personal data your organization has collected, processed, stored, or otherwise handled pertaining to my identity.</p>

<p>This request is made pursuant to, but not limited to, the following legal authorities:</p>

<ol class="statutes">
  <li><strong>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</strong>, Regulation (EU) 2016/679, in particular <strong>Article 17</strong> (Right to Erasure / &ldquo;Right to Be Forgotten&rdquo;);</li>
  <li><strong>GDPR Article 21</strong> &mdash; Right to Object to processing based on legitimate interests or direct marketing;</li>
  <li><strong>GDPR Article 7(3)</strong> &mdash; Right to withdraw consent at any time;</li>
  <li><strong>GDPR Article 15</strong> &mdash; Right of Access (I request confirmation of what data you hold);</li>
{% if jurisdiction == 'DE' %}
  <li><strong>German Federal Data Protection Act (BDSG)</strong>, &sect; 35 (Right to Erasure);</li>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'FR' %}
  <li><strong>French Data Protection Act (Loi Informatique et Libert&eacute;s)</strong>, as amended;</li>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'IT' %}
  <li><strong>Italian Data Protection Code (D.Lgs. 196/2003)</strong>, as amended by D.Lgs. 101/2018;</li>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'ES' %}
  <li><strong>Spanish Organic Law 3/2018 on Personal Data Protection (LOPDGDD)</strong>;</li>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'NL' %}
  <li><strong>Dutch GDPR Implementation Act (UAVG)</strong>;</li>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'GB' %}
  <li><strong>UK General Data Protection Regulation (UK GDPR)</strong> and <strong>Data Protection Act 2018</strong>;</li>
{% endif %}
  <li><strong>Charter of Fundamental Rights of the European Union</strong>, Article 8 (Protection of Personal Data);</li>
  <li><strong>ePrivacy Directive 2002/58/EC</strong>, as applicable.</li>
</ol>

<p>Pursuant to the above-cited authorities, I respectfully request that your organization take the following actions:</p>

<ol class="requests" type="a">
  <li><strong>Erase</strong> all personal data you hold about me, including any profiles, data compilations, behavioral records, and derivatives, in any format, whether collected directly or obtained from third-party sources (Article 17 GDPR);</li>
  <li><strong>Inform</strong> all recipients to whom personal data has been disclosed of this erasure request (Article 19 GDPR);</li>
  <li><strong>Cease</strong> all processing of my personal data, including any automated profiling, direct marketing, or data sharing with third parties;</li>
  <li><strong>Provide</strong> written confirmation of erasure and a list of all third parties with whom my data was shared (Articles 15 and 19 GDPR);</li>
  <li><strong>Confirm</strong> completion within <strong>30 days</strong> as mandated by Article 12(3) GDPR.</li>
</ol>

{% else %}
<p>I am writing to formally exercise my rights under applicable United States federal and state privacy and consumer protection laws. This letter constitutes a verified consumer request for the deletion of all personal information, personally identifiable information (PII), and consumer records your organization has collected, purchased, received, sold, shared, or otherwise processed pertaining to my identity.</p>

<p>This request is made pursuant to, but not limited to, the following statutes:</p>

<ol class="statutes">
{% if jurisdiction == 'IL' %}
  <li><strong>Illinois Personal Information Protection Act (PIPPA)</strong>, 815 ILCS 530/1 <em>et seq.</em>;</li>
  <li><strong>Illinois Biometric Information Privacy Act (BIPA)</strong>, 740 ILCS 14/1 <em>et seq.</em>;</li>
  <li><strong>Illinois Right of Publicity Act</strong>, 765 ILCS 1075/1 <em>et seq.</em>;</li>
  <li><strong>Illinois Consumer Fraud and Deceptive Business Practices Act</strong>, 815 ILCS 505/1 <em>et seq.</em>;</li>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'CA' %}
  <li><strong>California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)</strong>, Cal. Civ. Code &sect; 1798.100 <em>et seq.</em>, as amended by the <strong>California Privacy Rights Act (CPRA)</strong> of 2020;</li>
  <li><strong>California Online Privacy Protection Act (CalOPPA)</strong>, Bus. &amp; Prof. Code &sect; 22575;</li>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'TX' %}
  <li><strong>Texas Data Privacy and Security Act (TDPSA)</strong>, Tex. Bus. &amp; Com. Code &sect; 541;</li>
  <li><strong>Texas Identity Theft Enforcement and Protection Act</strong>, Tex. Bus. &amp; Com. Code &sect; 521;</li>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'NY' %}
  <li><strong>New York SHIELD Act</strong>, N.Y. Gen. Bus. Law &sect; 899-aa;</li>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'VA' %}
  <li><strong>Virginia Consumer Data Protection Act (VCDPA)</strong>, Va. Code &sect; 59.1-575 <em>et seq.</em>;</li>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'CO' %}
  <li><strong>Colorado Privacy Act (CPA)</strong>, Colo. Rev. Stat. &sect; 6-1-1301 <em>et seq.</em>;</li>
{% endif %}
{% if jurisdiction != 'CA' %}
  <li><strong>California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)</strong>, Cal. Civ. Code &sect; 1798.100 <em>et seq.</em>, as amended by the <strong>California Privacy Rights Act (CPRA)</strong> of 2020;</li>
{% endif %}
{% if jurisdiction != 'VA' %}
  <li><strong>Virginia Consumer Data Protection Act (VCDPA)</strong>, Va. Code &sect; 59.1-575 <em>et seq.</em>;</li>
{% endif %}
{% if jurisdiction != 'CO' %}
  <li><strong>Colorado Privacy Act (CPA)</strong>, Colo. Rev. Stat. &sect; 6-1-1301 <em>et seq.</em>;</li>
{% endif %}
  <li><strong>Connecticut Data Privacy Act (CTDPA)</strong>, Conn. Gen. Stat. &sect; 42-515 <em>et seq.</em>;</li>
{% if jurisdiction != 'TX' %}
  <li><strong>Texas Data Privacy and Security Act (TDPSA)</strong>, Tex. Bus. &amp; Com. Code &sect; 541;</li>
{% endif %}
  <li><strong>Oregon Consumer Privacy Act (OCPA)</strong>, ORS &sect; 646A.570 <em>et seq.</em>;</li>
  <li><strong>Fair Credit Reporting Act (FCRA)</strong>, 15 U.S.C. &sect; 1681 <em>et seq.</em>;</li>
  <li><strong>Federal Trade Commission Act</strong>, Section 5, 15 U.S.C. &sect; 45.</li>
</ol>

<p>Pursuant to the above-cited authorities, I respectfully request that your organization take the following actions:</p>

<ol class="requests" type="a">
  <li><strong>Delete</strong> all personal information, records, profiles, data compilations, and any derivatives thereof that you maintain about me, in any format, whether collected directly or obtained from third-party sources;</li>
  <li><strong>Direct</strong> all service providers, contractors, data brokers, affiliates, and third parties with whom you have shared, sold, or disclosed my personal information to likewise delete all such data;</li>
  <li><strong>Cease</strong> the sale, sharing, licensing, or other dissemination of my personal information, effective immediately;</li>
  <li><strong>Confirm</strong> in writing the completion of these actions within the time periods mandated by applicable law (45 calendar days under the CCPA/CPRA; 45 days under VCDPA, CPA, and CTDPA).</li>
</ol>
{% endif %}

{% if listing_urls %}
<div class="evidence-block">
  <strong>Documented Exposure</strong>
  <p style="margin: 8px 0 4px 0; font-size: 13px;">I have identified the following listing(s) on your platform containing my personal information:</p>
  <ul>
    {% for url in listing_urls %}<li><a href="{{ url }}">{{ url }}</a></li>{% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>
{% endif %}

{% if data_types_found %}
<p>Specifically, the following categories of personal data are being publicly displayed or processed by your organization: <strong>{{ data_types_found | join(', ') }}</strong>.</p>
{% endif %}

{% if privacy_policy_url %}
<div class="policy-note">
  I have reviewed your organization's privacy policy at <a href="{{ privacy_policy_url }}">{{ privacy_policy_url }}</a> and am exercising the rights described therein, in addition to the statutory rights cited above.
</div>
{% endif %}

<div class="info-block">
  <strong>Identifying Information</strong>
  <table>
    <tr><td class="info-label">Full Legal Name:</td><td>{{ full_name }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="info-label">Email Address:</td><td>{{ email }}</td></tr>
    {% if phone %}<tr><td class="info-label">Telephone:</td><td>{{ phone }}</td></tr>{% endif %}
    {% if address %}<tr><td class="info-label">Mailing Address:</td><td>{{ address }}</td></tr>{% endif %}
{% if region == 'EU' %}
    <tr><td class="info-label">Country of Residence:</td><td>{{ jurisdiction }}</td></tr>
{% elif jurisdiction and jurisdiction != 'US' %}
    <tr><td class="info-label">State of Residence:</td><td>{{ jurisdiction }}</td></tr>
{% endif %}
  </table>
</div>

<p>Should you require additional verification of my identity to process this request, please contact me at the email address provided above. I am happy to provide any reasonable documentation necessary to confirm my identity as the data subject.</p>

{% if region == 'EU' %}
<p>I appreciate your prompt attention to this matter. Please note that under Article 12(3) GDPR, you are required to respond within <strong>30 days</strong>. Failure to comply may result in a complaint to the relevant supervisory authority under Article 77 GDPR, which may impose administrative fines of up to &euro;20 million or 4% of annual global turnover under Article 83(5).</p>
{% else %}
<p>I appreciate your prompt attention to this matter and look forward to receiving written confirmation of compliance within the statutory timeframe. Please note that I reserve all rights afforded to me under the above-cited statutes, including the right to file a complaint with the appropriate regulatory authority in the event of non-compliance.</p>
{% endif %}

<div class="signature">
  <p>Respectfully yours,</p>
  <p>
    <strong>{{ full_name }}</strong><br>
    {{ email }}{% if phone %}<br>{{ phone }}{% endif %}
  </p>
</div>

<div class="cc-block">
{% if region == 'EU' %}
{% if jurisdiction == 'DE' %}
  cc: Bundesbeauftragte f&uuml;r den Datenschutz und die Informationsfreiheit (BfDI)<br>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'FR' %}
  cc: Commission Nationale de l&rsquo;Informatique et des Libert&eacute;s (CNIL)<br>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'IT' %}
  cc: Garante per la protezione dei dati personali<br>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'ES' %}
  cc: Agencia Espa&ntilde;ola de Protecci&oacute;n de Datos (AEPD)<br>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'NL' %}
  cc: Autoriteit Persoonsgegevens (AP)<br>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'GB' %}
  cc: Information Commissioner&rsquo;s Office (ICO)<br>
{% elif jurisdiction == 'IE' %}
  cc: Data Protection Commission (DPC)<br>
{% else %}
  cc: National Data Protection Authority<br>
{% endif %}
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;European Data Protection Board (EDPB)
{% else %}
  cc: Federal Trade Commission, Consumer Response Center<br>
{% if jurisdiction == 'IL' %}
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Illinois Attorney General, Consumer Protection Division
{% elif jurisdiction == 'CA' %}
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;California Privacy Protection Agency
{% elif jurisdiction == 'TX' %}
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Texas Attorney General, Consumer Protection Division
{% elif jurisdiction == 'NY' %}
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;New York Attorney General, Bureau of Internet and Technology
{% else %}
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Office of the State Attorney General
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
</div>

<div class="footer">
{% if region == 'EU' %}
  Ref: {{ request_id }} &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp; This communication constitutes a formal legal request under the General Data Protection Regulation (EU) 2016/679 and applicable data protection laws.
{% else %}
  Ref: {{ request_id }} &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp; This communication constitutes a formal legal request under applicable U.S. federal and state privacy laws.
{% endif %}
</div>

</body>
</html>
